The '''''Interceptor''''' was an [[Imperial Office of Customs/Legends|Imperial Customs]] [[Guardian-class light cruiser|''Guardian''-class light cruiser]] that had been assigned to patrol the [[Elin Roe system/Legends|Elin Roe system]] at some point during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was commanded by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Hallyn Phlynne]].<ref name="SL2">{{JournalCite|2|Smuggler's Log}}</ref>

